spec_data.Name: python2-django-openid-auth
spec_data.Description:
A library that can be used to add OpenID support to Django applications.
The library integrates with Django's built in authentication system, so
most applications require minimal changes to support OpenID login.
This package provides Python 2 build of django-openid-auth.
